@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram - BPO Management System Search

[*] --> FilterSelection

state "FilterSelection" as FS {
    [*] --> CategoryFilter : [Select category]
    [*] --> PriceRangeFilter : [Select price range]
}

FS : entry / User selects filter criteria
FS : do / Display matching users based on chosen criteria
FS : exit / Search completed

@enduml
